    <section id="pricing-compare" class="clearfix content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="title-content clearfix">
          <div class="title-inner">
            <h3>Per-Graft vs. Graft Bucket Pricing</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-grid pricing-grid-2 clearfix">
          <div class="pricing-col">
            <div class="white-bg padding pricing-compare-card">
              <i class="fa fa-thumbs-o-down"></i>
              <h4>Per-Graft Pricing</h4>
              <p>
                Initial cost can look lower, but total cost may escalate with
                over-quoting and extra charges.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-col">
            <div class="white-bg padding pricing-compare-card">
              <i class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up"></i>
              <h4>Graft Bucket Pricing</h4>
              <p>
                Fixed and transparent pricing with no hidden fees, guided by an
                expert consultation.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="pricing-faq" class="clearfix content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="title-content clearfix">
          <div class="title-inner">
            <p>Pricing</p>
            <h3>Pricing and Payment FAQs</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="white-bg padding pricing-faq-wrap">
          <details class="pricing-faq-item" open>
            <summary>What is the average cost of a hair transplant in the UK?</summary>
            <p>
              Hair transplant costs in the UK can vary widely depending on graft
              count, clinic expertise, and aftercare. Official Hair Clinic
              provides transparent fixed-package pricing so you know exactly
              what is included.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="pricing-faq-item">
            <summary>Can I get finance for my procedure?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes. We offer 0% financing options that allow you to spread the
              cost over manageable monthly payments.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="pricing-faq-item">
            <summary>How can I get an exact quote?</summary>
            <p>
              Your quote is confirmed after a surgeon-led consultation where we
              assess your hair loss pattern, donor capacity, and treatment plan.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="pricing-faq-item">
            <summary>Are aftercare and follow-up visits included?</summary>
            <p>
              Our packages include structured follow-up support so your recovery
              and growth progression are monitored properly.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="pricing-faq-item">
            <summary>Are online calculators accurate?</summary>
            <p>
              Calculators are useful for rough estimates, but they cannot replace
              a full surgeon consultation for a precise, personalised quote.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

